fhIu4M2F8b rebar-bot joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com"}],"bridge_alerts":[],"claim_harness":"claude-code_2-1-215_agent","claim_remote_session":null,"claimed_session":"5e1736fd-6a46-425f-96e3-3460f9fcb4f7","comments":[],"created_at":1783720475290031001,"creation_channel":"unknown","deps":[{"link_uuid":"1cd57dfe-f141-4f67-bffb-ada2e75e5fb8","relation":"discovered_from","target_id":"1d63-430a-1a70-4987"}],"description":"## Reproduction Steps\nDiscovered during the fix for dying-verastile-quelea (the observability probe going stale).\n`install-certbot-timer.sh` materializes a host artifact (systemd timer + any /usr/local/bin\nhelper) OUTSIDE the compose build context, exactly like `install-observability.sh`. The\nautodeploy loop only rebuilds the review-bot container (BOT_PATHS) and now re-materializes the\nobservability probe (OBS_PATHS); it does NOT refresh the certbot timer when\n`infra/scripts/install-certbot-timer.sh` changes.\n\n1. Change `infra/scripts/install-certbot-timer.sh` and land it.\n2. autodeploy advances `main` on the box but never re-runs the certbot installer.\n\n## Expected vs Actual\n- **Expected:** a change to the certbot-timer installer is materialized on the box on next deploy.\n- **Actual:** the installed certbot timer silently goes stale (same class as the observability bug).\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] autodeploy re-materializes the certbot timer when `infra/scripts/install-certbot-timer.sh`\n      (or its inputs) change between deployed..target — e.g. add it to a host-materialize trigger.\n- [ ] A hermetic regression test asserts the installer is re-invoked on a certbot-source change.\n- [ ] Decide + document whether `install-autodeploy.sh` (autodeploy's own installer / self-update)\n      should also be covered, or is deliberately excluded.","env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","file_impact":[],"keyring":[],"last_status_env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","managed_refs":[],"parent_id":null,"parent_status_uuid":"fb96b361-aa82-4f08-892f-41316ed8ddd9","preconditions_summary":{"status":"pre-manifest"},"priority":2,"reverts":[],"status":"in_progress","tags":[],"ticket_id":"c593-f058-c488-406c","ticket_type":"bug","title":"autodeploy does not re-materialize the certbot-timer host artifact on source change (sibling of dying-verastile-quelea)","verify_commands":[]},"source_event_uuids":["f2b2f493-93c0-4c41-8a45-fd2ed8a164b0","1cd57dfe-f141-4f67-bffb-ada2e75e5fb8","fb96b361-aa82-4f08-892f-41316ed8ddd9","0f4acfea-fd8f-4e35-be6b-52bcd25030e0","52a49a15-2f55-4e80-ad82-303717d9130e"]},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"SNAPSHOT","timestamp":1784488215784517476,"uuid":"0ab811c0-fef3-4470-8217-d727173e9ad2"}